  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Comprehensive child protection services for disaster affected children and adolescents in Jawzjan and Faryab Provinces.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Save the Children (SC) will implement a comprehensive package of Child Protection in Emergencies services, including specialized case management, capacity building, systems strengthening and PSS, in Jawzjan and Faryab Province targeting conflict affected children and adolescents, internally displaced and of the host communities. 
To prevent hypothermia, the project will provide winterization kits to severely and moderately acute malnourished under five children admitted in SC supported emergency mobile health and nutrition teams in Faryab, Jawzjan and Balkh provinces during the winter season.</narrative>
  </description>
